videos.description: Steph Curry penetrates and drops a nice look-away bounce pass to Kelly Oubre to throw down a powerful slam on the baseline.

videos.description: Steph Curry knocks down a big-time 3-point shot to put the Warriors up 115-110 on the Lakers with just over one minute left in the fourth quarter.

videos.description: The Warriors go on an astounding 14-2 run to secure a 115-113 comeback win over the champion Lakers on their home floor.
